                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/relg-407" class="program-course-title">
              RELG 407 The Writings (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-35055" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Religious Studies (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/614">Faculty of Religious Studies</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Religious Studies              : A study of Job with some attention to Proverbs and Ecclesiastes (in English translation).          </p>

