      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Religious Studies              : A study of the history, philosophy and practices of Vajrayana Buddhism.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

